</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>The dependent product of a family of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>20</fr:day></fr:date><fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-001B/0</fr:addr><fr:route>https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001B/0.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="dependent product of propositions › forest://erct/erct-001B/0"><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001B.xml" title="dependent product of propositions" addr="forest://erct/erct-001B" type="local">dependent product of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link></fr:link> › forest://erct/erct-001B/0</fr:title><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
  <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B \colon  A \to  \mathsf {Type}]]></fr:tex> be a family of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link>; fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f : \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex>, it suffices to show any other <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[g :\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}Bx]]></fr:tex> may be identified with <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>. As <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex> is a family of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">propositions</fr:link>, we know that each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Bx]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[fx]]></fr:tex>. Therefore, the closure of <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> types under dependent products (<fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001A.xml" title="dependent product of contractible types" addr="forest://erct/erct-001A" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-001A" /></fr:link>) shows that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}Bx]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
